  remove the ones that don't apply>.
- Never `git push` without explicit human instruction.

## Definition of done

A change is deliverable when: tests pass (real output shown), reviewers
returned APPROVED or all verified blockers are fixed, and the delivery
message lists residual non-blocking findings honestly.
